---
// Componente de CTA flotante que acompaña el scroll
---

<section class="sticky-cta-section">
  <div class="sticky-cta-container">
    <div class="cta-content">
      <h3 class="cta-title">Centralize Toda Sua Experiência</h3>
      <p class="cta-description">
        É comum ter sua experiência profissional dispersa em documentos, planilhas e memórias. 
        Com VitrinePro, você reúne tudo em um único lugar, pronto para impressionar o mundo.
      </p>
    </div>
    <a href="/VitrinePro-frontend/cadastro" class="cta-button">
      <span>Criar minha Vitrine</span>
      <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <path d="M13 7L19 13M19 13L13 19M19 13H5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
      </svg>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
:root {
  --vp-primary: #0A66C2;
  --vp-secondary: #004182;
  --vp-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--vp-primary), var(--vp-secondary));
}

.sticky-cta-section {
  position: fixed;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  background: var(--vp-gradient);
  color: white;
  padding: 20px 0;
  box-shadow: 0 -4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  z-index: 999;
  animation: slideUp 0.4s ease-out;
  opacity: 1;
  transition: opacity 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
}

@keyframes slideUp {
  from {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(100px);
  }
  to {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
}

.sticky-cta-container {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 20px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  gap: 2rem;
}

.cta-content {
  flex: 1;
}

.cta-title {
  font-size: 1.3rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin: 0;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  line-height: 1.3;
}

.cta-description {
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  margin: 0;
  opacity: 0.95;
  line-height: 1.5;
}

.cta-button {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  background: white;
  color: var(--vp-primary);
  text-decoration: none;
  padding: 12px 28px;
  border-radius: 50px;
  font-size: 1rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  white-space: nowrap;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.cta-button:hover {
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  background: #f5f5f5;
}

.cta-button svg {
  transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.cta-button:hover svg {
  transform: translateX(3px);
}

/* Responsive adjustments */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .sticky-cta-section {
    padding: 16px 0;
  }

  .sticky-cta-container {
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: stretch;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-content {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-title {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .cta-description {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .cta-button {
    width: 100%;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 14px 24px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .sticky-cta-section {
    padding: 12px 0;
  }

  .sticky-cta-container {
    padding: 0 16px;
  }

  .cta-title {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .cta-description {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .cta-button {
    padding: 12px 20px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .cta-button svg {
    width: 16px;
    height: 16px;
  }
}
</style>
